data.text: @ImjustagirlJm Looks like a pregnancy test, lol. Glad you are okay.

@flutterby2366 Thank you. It's definitely my allergy to leaf mold kicking up. All those leaves piled in ravines got moved by all the rain and I was out and about. My left eye is swollen up this morning.
@ImjustagirlJm Plus you are vaxd, even if (when) you do catch it should be mild. It’s endemic now so at some point now we’ll all get it.
@ImjustagirlJm My wife and I have done the same a few times. It’s nice to be sure.

@cec021 The duck at the Hob nob is to die for. The BCI is completely different and improved under new owners.  The Bird's Nest Cafe is a locals hang out...all food is made on site. ...as are the other two places I mentioned.  All are great.

@ImjustagirlJm Awesome, thank you. 
I like the fried chicken at The Brown County Inn.
@cec021 Brown County Inn... always something original on the menu. Hobnob on Main or Bird's Nest Cafe on Jefferson. All serve in house specialties.
@ImjustagirlJm Glad to hear you are negative. I'll be in your part of the world in 2 weeks. Do you have any restaurant recommendations?
@jojorobo58_jojo I agree... I was afraid to do the test.
